thief-backpack-category-chameleon-name = chameleon set
thief-backpack-category-chameleon-description =
    Master of disguise and deception. You are everyone and no one.
    Includes chameleon clothing set, and chameleon projector.
    Disguise as anyone and anything.

thief-backpack-category-tools-name = breacher set
thief-backpack-category-tools-description =
    A lil' C4 knockin' at your door, and the sound of jaws.
    No obstacle will stop you!
    Includes two C4, a multitool, remote signaller, jaws of life,
    advanced welder, engineering goggles, and insulated gloves.

thief-backpack-category-chemistry-name = anatomy set
thief-backpack-category-chemistry-description =
    You've peaked in physical conditioning, with implants ready.
    Includes a storage implanter, DNA scrambler implanter,
    ephedrine bottle, syringe, empty shaker, and omega soap

thief-backpack-category-syndie-name = syndicate set
thief-backpack-category-syndie-description =
    Trinkets from a disavowed past, or a careless agent.
    But you can never forget connections. Whiskey, echo...
    Includes an Agent ID card, Emag, syndicate pAI,
    Interdyne cigs, and some strange red crystals.

thief-backpack-category-sleeper-name = sleeper set
thief-backpack-category-sleeper-description =
    Space sleep disorder. Terminal. Until we close our eyes for good.
    Includes two tanks of sleepy nitrous oxide, two nocturine bottles,
    and a hypopen.

thief-backpack-category-communicator-name = communicator set
thief-backpack-category-communicator-description =
    Silver-tongued, wiretappin' back-alley dealer.
    Includes a master key for all station channels, CyberSun pen,
    voice chameleon mask, and 20k spesos inside a briefcase.

thief-backpack-category-smuggler-name = smuggler set
thief-backpack-category-smuggler-description =
    If you never stored your goods, were you ever a thief?
    Includes a fulton beacon, 10 fultons, 3 smoke grenades,
    and an invisible crate to hide valuable loot.
